        <li>• Enhanced sports content (select markets)</li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n            </div>\r\n\r\n            <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-green-50 to-emerald-50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-green-200\">\r\n              <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900\">🔧 Technology Improvements</h3>\r\n              <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700\">\r\n                <li>• Enhanced recommendation algorithms</li>\r\n                <li>• Improved user interface and navigation</li>\r\n                <li>• Expanded 4K/HDR content library</li>\r\n                <li>• Better integration between HBO and Discovery content</li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </section>\r\n\r\n        \r\n        <div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-pink-600 text-white rounded-xl p-8 text-center\">\r\n          <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-4\">Experience Premium Streaming</h2>\r\n          <p class=\"text-xl mb-6 text-purple-100\">\r\n            HBO's legendary content meets Discovery's vast library on Max\r\n          </p>\r\n          <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center\">\r\n            <a href=\"https://www.max.com\" class=\"bg-white text-purple-600 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-purple-50 transition-colors\">\r\n              Start Your Free Trial\r\n            </a>\r\n            <a href=\"https://www.max.com/plans\" class=\"bg-purple-500 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-purple-400 transition-colors border-2 border-white/30\">\r\n              Compare Plans\r\n            </a>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        \r\n        <div class=\"mt-12 pt-8 border-t-2 border-gray-200\">\r\n          <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900\">Related Streaming Services</h3>\r\n          <div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4\">\r\n            <a href=\"/entertainment/netflix\" class=\"text-center p-4 b